title: POP: Methodology Experiment One OST
description:
Rob Lach here...

I'm making the soundtrack for my award winning experimental indie game called POP: Methdology Experiment One free to pirate. 

I've gotten quite a few e-mails saying the music was one of the best parts of the game, and the game was designed around the music, so I hope you enjoy it.

If you like it or you'd like to support someone who makes this kind of stuff I invite you to purchase it.

The soundtrack is available for purchase on iTunes, Amazon, etc. It's also packaged with the game which can be bought directly from the game's website. It's actually cheaper to buy the game with the soundtrack included than the soundtrack by itself so I recommend just doing that (I don't completely control iTunes prices and whatnot).
